                source of vitamin A, D, K & E and also is a best friend of your
                kitchen who brings out the best version of any dish..
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="ingredients">
              <h3>
                <bold>SKU</bold>: 100ml , 200ml , 500ml, 1000ml, 5ltr, 15ltr
              </h3>
              <h3><bold>Nutrition Informations :</bold>(per 100 ml approx.)</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>1.Energy 816 Kcal</li>
                <li>2.Saturated Fat 58.0 g</li>
                <li>3.Vitamin A 3461 IU</li>
                <li>4.Fat 90.7 g</li>
                <li>5.Cholestrol 190 mg</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <div class="textContainer">
            <div class="title">
              <h1 style="font-weight: 900">Butter</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <p>
                Directly from the cow’s milk are the Barani Butter(s) made by
                churning fresh or fermented cream or milk. Made with quality
                ingredients, our butter gives you the taste you love, spreadable
                right out of the refrigerator. Butter is always unavoidable part
                of our diet from the time since record. Our butter(s) have a
                sweet, tender flavor and a rich composition that comes from our
                insistence on using only the finest, unadulterated and purest
                form of milk. With the rich composition of Vitamin A, D,& E, it
                is also used in producing our customer’s favorite.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="ingredients">
              <h3><bold>SKU</bold>: 500g,1kg and 15 kg</h3>
              <h3><bold>Nutrition Information :</bold>(per 100 gm approx..)</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>1.Energy 722 Kcal</li>
                <li>2.Total Fat 80 g</li>
                <li>3.Saturated Fat 51 g</li>
                <li>4.Cholestrol 180 mg</li>
                <li>5.Total Carbohydrates 0 g</li>
                <li>6.Protein 0.5 g</li>
                <li>7. Vitamin A 65 mcg</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
